description:
3-ingredient Vegan Ube Milkshake! Full recipe:  http://www.astigvegan.com/vegan-ube-milkshake

If you can't find Filipino purple yams, you could use the dehydrated version ube powder or the ready-made frozen purple yam. Both available at Filipino Asian grocery stores. You could also get the ube powder online: http://amzn.to/1OiTWiE

Vegan Ube Milkshake is my new "beat-the-heat" treat. Kain na, let's eat!

Song: "Take Me to the Casbah" from Acid Jazz Test Vol.2
